### Bayesian analysis



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
model <- brm(
  response ~ 0 + condition,
  data = data,
  family = gaussian(),
  prior = c(
    prior(normal(4, 1), class = "b"),
    prior(cauchy(1, 1), class = "sigma")
  ),
  file = "./models/model-between-subjects-group-difference.rds"
)
summary(model)
```

